- [examples/upwind/sailing_upwind.py](mdc:examples/upwind/sailing_upwind.py) - Upwind sailing algorithm
- [examples/downwind/sailing_downwind.py](mdc:examples/downwind/sailing_downwind.py) - Downwind sailing algorithm

## Development Notes

- Uses Cython for performance-critical components
- Coordinate system follows trigonometric circle convention (0° = East, 90° = North)
- Simulation timestep is 0.1 seconds
- All angles must be integers when passed to Manager.step()